# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# This app uses file-based JSON storage by default (data/projects.json).
# No environment variables are required for local development or for running
# on a persistent Node host such as a Hostinger VPS.
#
# If you later move the backend to a managed Postgres database (recommended
# when deploying the API on Vercel, whose serverless filesystem is ephemeral),
# add your connection string here and implement a PostgresRepository behind the
# ProjectRepository interface in src/lib/storage.ts:
#
# DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@host:5432/dbname?schema=public"
# STORAGE_DRIVER="postgres"
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
